    <title></title>
    <link href="/2024/01/21/%E5%9C%A8ubuntu%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85matplotlibcpp/"/>
    <url>/2024/01/21/%E5%9C%A8ubuntu%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85matplotlibcpp/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><p>环境为ubuntu20.04远程服务器</p></li><li><p>下载地址：</p><p><a href="https://github.com/lava/matplotlib-cpp.git">https://github.com/lava/matplotlib-cpp.git</a></p></li><li><p>检查系统是否安装了python3，python3-dev，python-numpy，若没有请按照如下命令安装</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">sudo apt-get install python3 python3-dev python-numpy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>编译安装</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd matplotlib-cpp-master<br>mkdir build &amp;&amp; cd build<br>cmake ..<br>make<br>sudo make install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译安装成功后如图下图</p><img src="在ubuntu安装matplotlibcpp/截屏2024-01-21 21.27.34.png" width = 100%><ul><li>安装后应在&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;include目录下看到matplotlibcpp.h文件</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  
